high_descs: walk over to the white table
grab the spatula off of the table
back up a bit from the table
place the spatula inside the blue bowl on the table
pick up the blue bowl off of the table
move a bit to the left of the table
place the blue bowl down on the black table next to the white table
anns.task_desc: place a blue bowl with a spatula in it down on the black table

high_descs: Turn around, look down at the table
Grab the spatula from the table
Walk towards the left, still looking at the table
Place the spatula in the bucket on the table
Grab the bucket from the table
Walk towards the black table next to the white table
Place the bucket on top of the black table
anns.task_desc: Place the bucket with the utensils on the black table

high_descs: Turn left and face toward the white table
Pick up the spatula behind the box from the table
Turn left then face back toward the same white table
Put the spatula into the blue bowl on the table
Pick up the blue bowl from the table
Move slightly left to face the small dark table just left of the white table
Put the blue bowl down on the small dark table
anns.task_desc: Put the blue bowl with spatula on the small dark table
